_:B137995a35e6f05b9229da75b1502e80c <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#annotatedTarget> "The pituitary gland is an endocrine gland that secretes hormones that regulate many other glands [GO]. An endocrine gland located ventral to the diencephalon and derived from mixed neuroectodermal and non neuroectodermal origin [ZFIN]." .
_:B137995a35e6f05b9229da75b1502e80c <http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "Wikipedia:Pituitary_gland" .
