_:B3ecb598010578d9b53230d80e0a8b1f3 <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#annotatedTarget> "Either of a pair of glandular pouches that lie one on either side of the male reproductive tract posterolateral to the urinary bladder and in the human male secrete a sugar- and protein-containing fluid into the ejaculatory duct." .
_:B3ecb598010578d9b53230d80e0a8b1f3 <http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "BTO:0001234" .
